Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's 1955.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.59,0:00:09.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After recovering from\N the chaos of defeat, Japanese society
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.47,0:00:12.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is about to enter a period\N of rapid economic growth,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,alongside an explosive rise in consumer culture.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.52,0:00:19.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a love story of the young people
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.74,0:00:22.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who hung out near Shonan Beach around that time. {https://maps.app.goo.gl/fKAKQQkus46K9FEv5}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.46,0:00:28.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These teenagers who unleashed their raw energy upon the world
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.02,0:00:30.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,were called the "Children of the Sun." {taiyouzoku = tribe of the sun}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.04,0:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get it. She's the one that sent you\N the flowers before the match.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,Why'd she wear a kimono\N to a boxing match?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.81,0:01:13.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,This isn't a picnic. {flower viewing}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Tsugawa-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.53,0:01:23.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'd met Eiko on Saturday, \Nfive days earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.03,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.32,0:01:30.82,Overlap,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,We went to town for some fun,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,We couldn't afford\N the professional girls,{not sure if the official TL is cooking here, but he means prostitutes}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.77,0:01:39.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,so we thought we'd try \Nto pick up some normal girls. {shirouto = honest/respectable woman}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm from the Meisei\N University Sports Club...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.39,0:01:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, I'm Tatsuya Tsugawa from the Boxing Club.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a boxer?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.26,0:01:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A featherweight.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.96,0:02:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We were hoping that you could hang out with us for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know any girls in this town, so we were in a pickle. Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We promise to behave ourselves. {lit: not deal you inconvenience}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're free, won't you please go out with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.99,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you won't be disappointed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.09,0:02:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.17,0:02:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.78,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,6!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,7!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,8!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.45,0:03:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the flowers, but please don't make such a fuss anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're distracting me from fighting.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to see you too. {?? dunno what she means by "oh, greeting"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew you'd be so tough?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you wearing a kimono?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the other girls?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They went home.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,After that, we met a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,You'd be surprised \Nhow many friends Eiko had.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,A lot of them were men too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,But I didn't care.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning to commit to this relationship.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a girl here to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a looker.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to be passing by.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.02,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Happened"?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost summer, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to Hayama \Nto prepare our summerhouse. {https://maps.app.goo.gl/2wR7BgFG6KcFei6UA}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go sailing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going back to Tokyo tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long drive, so I'll probably stay in Hayama tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can stay at my place.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a bath, dinner, and a good rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I need to take a bath first.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, you can wait here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.65,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you punch\N that sandbag. Right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening with\N Eiko-san these days?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.76,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing much, really. \NBut I see her a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it was you dancing with her\N at the Katsupi Club two days ago? {really sounds like katsuki here, but later it's closer to Katsupi; can't find either on the map}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've called you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Two days ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My old man frequents this place to entertain clients,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.51,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so I often tag along and take advantage of his tab.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugawa, he's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who was with Eiko at the Katsupi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.64,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The show-off, \Nover with that laughing girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.92,Top,,0,0,0,,Come on, Matsumoto-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Matsumoto-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.21,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the bandmaster and trumpeter \Nfor the Five Roses band. {?? unsure, maybe "bandmaster" is part of the band name}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.36,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, they perform at Katsupi, \Nalways playing to a full house.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugawa, don't start anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll just step on his toes a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.73,0:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I hit you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I stepped on your foot?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole! Don't pretend you don't know!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya, you're jealous!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Summer, my favorite season,\Nhad finally arrived.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. Such a nice song at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad there's no room to dance here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sea sparkle! {Noctiluca scintillans (luminescent species of dinoflagellate)}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a sea devil. {football fish (any fish of family Himantolophidae, esp. the Atlantic footballfish, Himantolophus groenlandicus)}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on in!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Something bright swam past me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a jellyfish.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.47,0:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the boat. I'm scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.53,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a sissy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.23,0:11:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nights like this that make me believe in those cheesy stories about the moon. {? no idea what she's talking about}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You asleep, Tatsu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.11,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only eleven, and there's a party at the hotel tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.70,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a golden opportunity! \NLet's go hunting for virgins. {trusting officials; lit: long live the young girls exterminatory measure; eradication campaign}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.40,0:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. See you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.16,0:12:44.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,No matter where I went, Eiko always showed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.52,0:12:50.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,We played around in the water naked at night, but that's not our usual life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:11.68,Song,,0,0,0,,{the end credits list "涙のスクリーン / namida no screen" song by da capo as insert, but https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u0LVUblLZMI doesn't sound like this; anidb lists ため息 / tameiki by da capo as insert, but this doesn't sound like https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rdMxjiaE3FI either; regardless, safe to assume it's some song by da capo, but there's no way to establish which one, and there are no lyrics for it out there; in any case, going by ear}But if kindness is too much, \Nthen how many loves can there be? {??? very unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good trip! {no clue but it's something about the wind, so probably "may you have favorable wind" as in "fare well" since they're sailing}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks. {still no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump in, Sally.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:25.32,Song,,0,0,0,,Love is parched like hot desert sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:34.74,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if called a crow's affection, \NI don't mind being refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:42.76,Song,,0,0,0,,May our two loves overlap, entwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:55.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Midsummer youth, cradled in my heart... {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.45,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiko's with me now.\NShe's no longer into you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.40,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to make excuses\N just 'cause she slept with you once.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.68,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All I've gotta do is crook my finger, \Nand she'll come running back to me. {/if I just called to her}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's see you do it tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it and she dumps me, \NI'll give you 5,000 yen. {lit: if I'm out}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she refuses, \Nyou'll fork it out yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In either case, think of it \Nas severance pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't add conditions now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.81,0:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Tatsuya, I want you out of here today.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay, it'll make things difficult later on.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.34,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the mountains. \NI'll pay for the trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.06,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. If you want her that bad, \NI'll sell her to you for 5,000. {factually, deal had already happened so has to be in past tense ig}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.26,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deal!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,I made myself scarce.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.52,0:15:42.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,Then I went to a boxing club training camp in Niigata.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,The summer finally came to an end.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boring here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Tatsuya is?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not interested in you anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.82,0:15:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.00,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man of his word.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What word?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.74,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to ask him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go for another swim.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at all the girls waiting for us! {lit: they came, we're popular!}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.76,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the training camp, the thing I missed most wasn't food or women.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was this sunset in the city.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your promise to Michihisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd ask me about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.43,0:16:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tacchan, does that mean you sold me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.91,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For 5,000 yen, I promised my brother that I wouldn't lay a finger on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd agree to that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was between me and my brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.86,0:17:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the money?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.77,0:17:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make sure\N to pay Michihisa back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.00,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But what will you do if we make another such agreement?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter. I'll keep on paying until you guys give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to do it again?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying so hard to hurt me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.65,0:17:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really hated me, you wouldn't go through all this trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you still love me, despite all that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.46,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why can't you just love me, \Nwithout all the pretense?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I couldn't do it either.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.03,0:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But after that night, I knew I could only truly love you. {lit: only do that to you}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.79,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've both been hurt before,\N just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.79,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can change that!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The same deal, one more time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.16,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just send it to her and she'll pay you for it as many times as you want. {?? i assume he means to her}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little guilty.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She blew you off, right? {/gave you a cold shoulder}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to pay her\N back in kind, sign here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.13,0:18:34.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected, \NEiko sent him the money again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.12,0:18:41.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,After that, I kept sending the contract\N to my reluctant brother to get him to sign,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,and Eiko always paid it back the same day.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.73,0:18:49.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,But I got a strange feeling,\N once the total reached 20,000 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not feeling good?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pregnant. \NThat's what I wanted to tell you today.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm three months in. \NIt's gotta be yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I have it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.78,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have the baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then have it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.01,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's the champ.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's completely different outside the ring.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's like this, he's finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.10,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long before he starts his fall from glory. {lit: saying goodbye to the champion belt is a matter of time}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.52,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind. \NI don't want a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected you to say that sooner or later.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It cramps my style. {/embarrassing/unseemly}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.42,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's dead?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was four days after her Caesarean.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She developed peritonitis.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The funeral will be\N the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.88,0:21:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Then why can't you just love me, \Nwithout all the pretense?"
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:37.56,Song,,0,0,0,,I write a letter to my loved one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:44.48,Song,,0,0,0,,I write and tear it, tear it, and write again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:51.03,Song,,0,0,0,,I throw the rolled up paper at the window
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:58.20,Song,,0,0,0,,It's raining outside, just like the tears on my cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:06.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Life is a sea, youth is a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:13.15,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, please come and save me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:15.57,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:18.68,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:26.83,Song,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm sinking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:36.25,Song,,0,0,0,,Not a single star in sight, in the sea of ​​sadness
